metadata.name: Don't mess with the Google Maps driver.
metadata.description:
This is a 1/1 authenticate NFT of an original performance by Loosii Ninjas. 

In 2021 the artist was seen on Google Street View being chased by the Google Maps car. As the creator and publisher of this viral performance seen on Street View this video is the first of original media being released by the artist. 

Shortly after being subject to a top trending Reddit thread this video became a viral meme. Along with several new headlines the video adopted titles such as "Don't mess with the Google Maps Driver". 

In retaining all the original imagery and intellectual property, this NFT represents the artists work as it has entered the public domain. 

Dimensions: 720 x 1280
Codecs: Timecode, H.264, AAC
Duration: 00:06
